    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Ready to impress! This well-maintained vehicle is in great shape and has plenty of life left to give. The paint holds up nicely with only minor signs of everyday use, the interior is clean and comfortable, and mechanically it runs smoothly and reliably. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's genuinely solid \u2014 the kind of car you can depend on day in and day out without worry. A fantastic value for a buyer who wants quality without the mint-condition price tag!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition \u2014 a used car that has seen its share of everyday use and shows it honestly. The exterior displays visible scratches, some paint fading, and a few minor dents that are noticeable upon close inspection. The interior has worn upholstery, scuffs on trim panels, and signs of regular use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though prospective buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term. This is a straightforward, no-surprises listing \u2014 what you see is what you get, priced accordingly for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and understands they're purchasing a well-used vehicle.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget Buy Alert \u2014 Great for the Right Hands! This vehicle is priced to move and represents a genuine opportunity for a mechanically inclined buyer or someone looking for an affordable project. We'll be upfront: this car is in poor condition, showing significant cosmetic wear, some mechanical issues, and the kind of character that comes from years of hard use. It does have potential \u2014 with some TLC and the right repairs, it could be back on the road. If you're handy with tools or looking for a parts car, this could be exactly what you need at a price that won't break the bank!",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should approach with realistic expectations and a clear understanding of what they're getting. The exterior shows considerable wear throughout: paint is faded and dulled in multiple areas, there are visible scratches, scuffs, and surface rust in several spots, and a few dents are present on the body panels. The interior reflects heavy use over the years \u2014 upholstery is worn and stained, trim pieces show cracking and discoloration, and some components may not function as originally intended. Mechanically, the car runs and can be driven, but it will require attention and likely some repairs to bring it up to a more reliable standard. This is best suited for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle, someone looking for basic transportation on a tight budget, or a parts donor. We are pricing it accordingly and transparently \u2014 no surprises, no inflated claims. What you see is what you get.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we're proud to give you an honest and complete picture of what you're getting. The exterior presents well \u2014 paint retains most of its original luster with only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal use, and the body panels are free of significant dents or rust. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing light wear but no major tears or damage; all controls, windows, and climate systems function as expected. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues \u2014 this is a car that has been maintained and is ready for daily driving. Tires have good tread remaining, brakes are in solid working order, and the suspension feels tight and responsive. Overall, this is a dependable, well-kept vehicle that offers strong value for a buyer looking for quality without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
