      "description": "\ud83d\udc8e $47,500 - A true showstopper for the buyer who demands the best! \u2728 This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 flawless inside and out, with every system running in perfect order. The paint shines like new, the interior is spotless, and mechanically it's as tight as the day it rolled off the lot. If you've been waiting for a pristine, move-in-ready ride with zero compromises, your search ends here! \ud83d\ude97",
